. Don't you think it was foolish, but you know it was good to have the biggest family in the village. They all had huge families. Oh dear, there was a lot of people - children went to school. I think there was two hundred and forty children in our school.
 Yes. Well - and the surrounding countryside - country and all you know, the - the country children we called them.
