re again, the war had - was on, and they couldn't - you - well it - they couldn't very well entertain, you know, they stopped people - baking all fancy cakes and all that sort of thing you know, so it was quiet after that you know, quiet for me so - I did
n't - I didn't stay a great long time there. And from there I went to Lady Ewarts, see. Yes. And then -
