e a - he was his own boss you know. He had part - his share of the water you see, they all had a shore of the - this - and then they would go fishing and - throw out their nets you know, when there was salmon come up the river and - they used to live on w
hat - what they made you know. Sometimes we had a lot and sometimes we had nothing you know.
