aces and - there was gentry there as I tell you, they used to fish - gentlemen used to fish on the river with a rod you know. Well my father was the boatman, he used to take - carry - take them out in the river in the boat you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 He did that during the closed season?
