{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Cheviot Hills{\*\xmlclose}
 and - when the rain comes on there you know it swells the river up and you get a great shoal of fish you know, yes, oh yes. I - when it was good season. But - it's just a gamble you know. Isn't it you know, when - when you're like that, when 
you have to depend on - on what you get. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 Do you remember your father being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2780120 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 
