s. In these big families you know, oh it was terrible. Ah well, we -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 How many rooms did you have downstairs?
