Oh well, just one great big room. And a - and a scullery. And a nice big pantry and that's all. But we had to have - well we had - well the bed was a sort of recess you see. Me father and mother's bed was in a sort of a recess - downstairs, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 They used to just pull it down?
