Well - it depends - oh not - not the great big pans, no. The big pans, but - sometime
s they would be on the floor you know. A great big pan of broth you know, she would ladle it out - into plates you see and put it round, that was the broth. But - the vegetables was put on the table, potatoes and - and the vegetables in the dishes like.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 What order were you served in, who got the first helping?
