\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid90349\charrsid1197286 be any}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286  particular - maybe the young ones first you know to get them setting on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 Where did the younger brothers and sisters sit before they could feed themsel
ves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2780120 ES  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 
Oh - either on mother's knee or - after she got us all served she would take them on her knee - take them on her knee.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 She fed them did she?
