\ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid90349\charrsid1197286  was a Captain and - and the Mis}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 
sus, Capt and Mrs. Tipping was called, they lived a little bit away from Norham but - used to come - about the school you know and used to 
always give us a party at Christmas, and I tell you all beautiful Christmas of the - off the Christmas tree. And he used to give prizes at school as well, for the best - yes, they did. Oh -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 It seemed to be a nice area to be living in?
