\ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid90349\charrsid1197286 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 
d used to play, real old Scotch songs like - Annie Laurie and these sort of things you know. Eeh it was nice you know.
