Oh yes, we had - we had the - the Berwick Advertiser every day. The Berwick Advertiser every day. Then I used to get the Girls Friend and - I was about - I was at school, I used to buy the Girls Friend in the village, yes, I liked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 Do you remember your mother or father reading?
