ed. Yes. And - we used to go on those days in the farm carts. Three big long farm carts that used to be taken - that used to take the - the grain in, you know, them - the - the sheaves and well we used to get in the - the horses were all dressed up you kn
ow so nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 Who used to go then?
