All the church Sunday school. Our church Sunday school, yes, yes. And it was lovely. And were all - they were - the horses were all dressed up and - they were grand horses, led by a farmer you know. And - they use
d to cart us all there, oh dear me, it was a real treat. But now they go in a - buses now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 It's not as much fun is it?
