Well I used to have to - oh they were all sorts you know, sweep the front door and - and wash the steps and things like that you know and wash the dishes and - and - set the tables and - clear the table you know and - and carry the food into the parlour.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid2116411 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286 What hours did you work?
