 you know, what do they call them again, basset hounds, and used to follow - around for rabbits and things when he had them basset - basset hounds and well and he used to go running about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid8261662\charrsid1197286 after}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7429624\charrsid1197286  rabbits and that. And - well he had that, all them things, hun
